{"tha-ap295:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap295:0.2":"Citakapujakavagga ","tha-ap295:0.3":"Chattadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap295:1.1":"“Putto mama pabbajito, ","tha-ap295:1.2":"kasayavasano tada; ","tha-ap295:1.3":"So ca buddhattam sampatto, ","tha-ap295:1.4":"nibbuto lokapujito. ","tha-ap295:2.1":"Vicinanto sakam puttam, ","tha-ap295:2.2":"agamam pacchato aham; ","tha-ap295:2.3":"Nibbutassa mahantassa, ","tha-ap295:2.4":"citakam agamasaham. ","tha-ap295:3.1":"Paggayha anjalim tattha, ","tha-ap295:3.2":"vanditva citakam aham; ","tha-ap295:3.3":"Setacchattanca paggayha, ","tha-ap295:3.4":"aropesim aham tada. ","tha-ap295:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap295:4.2":"yam chattamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap295:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap295:4.4":"chattadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap295:5.1":"Pancavise ito kappe, ","tha-ap295:5.2":"satta asum janadhipa; ","tha-ap295:5.3":"Maharahasanama te, ","tha-ap295:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap295:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap295:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap295:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap295:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma chattadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap295:8.1":"Chattadayakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}